4,"uid":79823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T10:00:12.000Z","msg":"買個靚焗爐，然後用電飯煲/大煲蒸野算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c46e23c97942ed81748ea12d334e76cf6f1593","tid":1980314,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T10:02:47.000Z","msg":"買座枱焗爐最好 <br />\n好似外國個d焗爐加熱好撚慢同好曬電 根本用唔到咁大 <br />\n除非你餐餐好似鬼佬咁焗野或者成日整麵包甜品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a1f8c8494da02abd297b6ef94c52b4fa7d01cc","tid":1980314,"uid":91918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:59:28.000Z","msg":"有位一定係買靚焗爐，蒸嘢你用火又得，係啲人廚房細（我）先要買蒸焗爐"}]}